campaigns.title: ahmed abo ali
campaigns.description: Love is one of the most beautiful and powerful emotions a person can experience. It connects hearts and gives life a true meaning. Love is based on understanding, respect, and mutual support, making people feel safe and comfortable. When someone loves sincerely, they are willing to make sacrifices for the happiness of their loved ones and share both joys and sorrows. Love is not limited to romantic relationships; it also includes love for family, friends, and even self-love. It inspires us to give generously without expecting anything in return and helps us see the world in a brighter light. Love represents forgiveness and acceptance, strengthens social bonds, and creates an environment of peace and harmony. Ultimately, love is the essence of life and the heartbeat that fills us with hope and joy, reminding us that life is more beautiful when shared with those we care about.

campaigns.title: ahmed abo sayed
campaigns.description: I’m curious what 150 words actually looks like on a page. I’m requiring my video production students to write a blog post each week for their 20 time projects. These blog posts need to have a least 150 words and an image that they have permission to use. When I first introduced this to the class last week and I mentioned 150 words, I could hear a corporate gasp. It was an utter shock. “Did he really say 150? That’s insane… 150 words is like an essay. It’s too much. How does he expect us to do that every week? Holy moly.” It was as if nearly every student thought that sounded like a short novel. I thought I’d set out to write 150 words in less than 5 minutes. Not only do I plan to write these words that quickly, I also will write them without much content. Done.

campaigns.description: It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout. The point of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal distribution of letters, as opposed to using 'Content here, content here', making it look like readable English. Many desktop publishing packages and web page editors now use Lorem Ipsum as their default model text, and a search for 'lorem ipsum' will uncover many web sites still in their infancy. Various versions have evolved over the years, sometimes by accident, sometimes on purpose (injected humour and the like).
